{"tid":1695203,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［黑警入大直路］黑警會係短時間用高壓武力 令你麻木，產生無力感","createTime":"2019-11-05T13:29:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T04:46:05.000Z","uid":11454,"like":266,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"1e2455dd378214a0e939a46b7b6094d90d763d3d","tid":1695203,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:29:12.000Z","msg":"三千人被捕<br />\n依兩日瘋狂吹風黑警止暴有效<br />\n每周濫捕幾百人<br />\n平日和平集會出水炮<br />\n食環都出黎清連儂牆<br />\n<br />\n總總跡象顯示，黑警同政權深信運動有降溫跡象<br />\n喺各位手足開始感覺迷失嘅時候<br />\n希望用最後高壓手段，以快打慢<br />\n將我哋多個月來既抗爭終結<br />\n<br />\n千祈千祈唔好俾依種種無力感支配<br />\n嚟緊呢幾個禮拜，將會受到史無前例<br />\n最黑暗，最卑鄙，最殘忍既手段攻擊<br />\n<br />\n記住我地團結一致，一定會贏！<br />\n崇高既理念係無堅不摧！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！"},{"pid":"55516f84f25e5902d4d5c066f105e7616871e472","tid":1695203,"uid":1655,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:30:51.000Z","msg":"就咁睇今晚都知冇冷卻到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af783fd1081ef0660d60842e5b6351528fe03bd0","tid":1695203,"uid":166506,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:31:11.000Z","msg":"團結<br />\n唔好比人佢地打擊到！"},{"pid":"0f53278cca60e6e44195f1d4840f93beb74ba4c4","tid":1695203,"uid":11454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"af783fd1081ef0660d60842e5b6351528fe03bd0","tid":1695203,"uid":166506,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:31:11.000Z","msg":"團結<br />\n唔好比人佢地打擊到！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:39:16.000Z","msg":"一定要團結<br />\n令更多人站係我地依邊"},{"pid":"c394718e9a9262caf795a4cc2d3e103cf81a5e59","tid":1695203,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:40:07.000Z","msg":"一秒破解<br />\n繼續出"},{"pid":"4a40297f7f103b08f49d0f9f3c793f234e74c706","tid":1695203,"uid":78085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:47:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f6fcb646aec579fbcc9e43a975450fe4bc719851","tid":1695203,"uid":41507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":